sequenceDiagram
  participant U as user
  participant R as Agent Runtime
  participant M as Model
  participant T as Tool System
  participant S as State

  U->>R: Submit task: fix test failure
  R->>S: Read the current task site
  R->>M: Build input for this round
  M-->>R: Return action intent: read package.json
  R->>T: Verify and execute read_file
  T-->>R: Return file content
  R->>S: Record tool results
  R->>M: Carry the observations into the next round
  M-->>R: Return to next step: running tests
